        "mainbody": "'''Manferic III''' was the king of [[Ankhapur]].",
        "Personality": "Manferic's goal was immortality but for his vanity he also wanted to maintain a good appearance and continue ruling his city.",
        "History": "Manferic ruled Ankhapur with an iron hand and a touch of sadism. In [[1366 DR]], he became a [[lich]] and started a plot to obtain the body of his bastard son [[Janol Famisso]] to inhabit. However, in the end, Janol proved to be more capable than him and Manferic was destroyed by Janol and his allies."
